Open browser
Click Communicator/AddressBook
In new window, click File/New Directory
Description: Whatever
LDAP Server: ebayldap1.ebay.sun.com
	or
			centralldap1.central.sun.com
Server Root: dc=sun, dc=com
Port Number: 389
OK

Type in a string into "Show names containing:"
listing will begin.
Double click on a name and a complete listing of attributes 
will be displayed.


